        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Preserving Patient Access to Home Infusion Act</b></p> <p>This bill specifically includes pharmacy services as part of covered home infusion therapy under Medicare, and specifies that certain payment components still apply regardless of whether or not a qualified supplier is physically present in the beneficiary's home. The bill also allows nurses and physician assistants to establish and review the plan of care for home infusion therapy. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
